# Quality Gates

Before writing **any** code, run these in order. Every step must exit 0.

**After a pause, a failure, or switching back to implementation:** run this full list again (see `.cursor/rules/pipeline-contract.mdc`).

## Code quality

```bash
npm run typecheck
npm run lint
npm run test:unit
npm run format:check
```

## RULEBOOK infrastructure

```bash
test -f docs/rulebook/RULEBOOK.md
grep -q "DEFINICION" docs/rulebook/RULEBOOK.md
```

## On failure

1. Stop — do not implement past the failure.
2. Read the tool output; fix the reported issue.
3. Re-run the failed gate until it passes.
4. Only then continue.
